name: MORPHEUS
description:
Known as the god of dreams, Morpheus is tasked with making dreams of every human on Earth. Sometimes the gods also sent him as a messenger conveyed through dreams.

Reported by Greek Gods and Goddess, Morpheus used to carry out his duties in human form. Don't let you see it in its original form, okay? Because Morpheus looks like a demon with wings
